title: help plz lag
body: start with 90 fps after 20 25 min 30-50 fps help

replies.body: Hmmmm there's a chance that those fps were caused by some kind of weird file interaction. We should be able to figure out the main issue by going through the steps in our [**FPS guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752684-Low-Frame-Rate-FPS-Troubleshooting), but hit me back up if that doesn't do the trick!
